{"tid":625034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屙屎冇廁紙可以點做","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T07:19:27.000Z","uid":87088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ffd150ea40f4cb1f596e53759baba09d9ceae5","tid":625034,"uid":87088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"話說今日人有三急，bang bang聲衝左入公司廁所<br />\n話說之前已經三日冇野出，衣家一出真係猶如山泥傾瀉咁，個種感覺就好似一個好唔受歡迎既同事煩左你三個月，終於走左<br />\n但係，正當我諗住敏個靚屎既時候<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n冇廁紙！<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/140737_3d8a90ac0a1fa331ee495a83b43fe8ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F140737_3d8a90ac0a1fa331ee495a83b43fe8ad.png&h=aed52d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來想出去攞紙巾，但出面幾個契弟係咁吹水<br />\n打比同事又好尷尬<br />\n想問下各位有冇試過用呢隻紙去敏，效果如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/141321_ce4ab1022ebd750485b45adec91c5513.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F141321_ce4ab1022ebd750485b45adec91c5513.png&h=5d904d92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a74755126d66cfc8e43d7d6e870f1813c408bf50","tid":625034,"uid":116714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"用手指，再洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805f96f17fe9fbcafff7f277414792ad71f4269f","tid":625034,"uid":106333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"用底褲 之後掉左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc39c890ef959ccaf7840569cf2217399b7542b","tid":625034,"uid":106018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim